title: My Cousin Trendy 12/8: Airpods Max, COVID Outbreak, Vaccine Line, Cyberpunk 2077, Mall Santa
itunes:title: My Cousin Trendy 12/8: Airpods Max, COVID Outbreak, Vaccine Line, Cyberpunk 2077, Mall Santa
description:
On this edition of My Cousin Trendy Jack, Miles and DJ Danl discuss Apple releasing over-ear Airpods Max, Jenna Ellis has contracted COVID, what place in line are you to get a Vaccine, Cyberpunk 2077 comes out tomorrow, and Right Wing Media is freaking out over a mall Santa video.
